Summary:
The player has been tasked with convincing the Ambassadors of the Freestar Collective and House Va'ruun to help the United Colonies gain access to the Armistice Archives. The player can gain their consent - or not - and then access the Archives to collect the Terrormorph data Hadrian has requested and hopes will be the key to stopping the Terrormorphs.

One big note - this mission comes after a major Terrormorph attack on New Atlantis (deadly aliens) and so all the scenes should be informed by that. Folks are looking to act and make things right.
